                                  ey-integrity
    Deploy a continuous integration server onto http://cloud.engineyard.com

USAGE

Ask beta@engineyard.com or email me directly at simon@rozet.name to get access
to the PostgreSQL beta program.

  * Create a new Rack application for git://github.com/sr/ey-integrity.git
  * Add bundler 0.9.25 and Rack 1.1.0 to the gems
  * Attach the app to a Nginx+Unicorn and PostgreSQL environment.
  * Upload the custom recipes with `ey-recipes -u ENV`
  * Hit deploy on the dashboard
